"/> is 6."
msgstr ""
"<img src=\"%(url_round)s\" />计算数字的圆整值。也就是把小数四舍五入成整数。例如：<img "
"src=\"%(url_round_5_1)s\" />等于5，<img src=\"%(url_round_5_6)s\" />等于6。"

#: templates/help/studio/tips/blocks/say-for-seconds.html:8
